'''Energy web generators''' produced a network of lightning-like energy that arced from the weapon and assailed its target, much like an [[Ion cannon/Legends|ion cannon]] burst. They were used aboard the [[Aing-Tii/Legends|Aing-Tii's]] [[Sanhedrim ship]]s.

